 s from the IU Eskenazi School Studio Art BA class of 2026. The works on v
 iew draw from a range of media and influences from the different areas th
 roughout the Studio Art program. The artists on view explore a range of c
 ontent and subject matter to create projects that act as the culminating 
 experience of their time in the Eskenazi School of Art\, Architecture\, a
 nd Design at IU.
