SUMMARY:Interior Design Capstone Show
DESCRIPTION:For the last 15 weeks\, students have developed designs for t
 enants in a hypothetical community centerŌĆöfocusing on the complexities 
 of developing community\, supporting people across populations\, ethicall
 y building\, and technically meet construction and code requirements. The
  Capstone Show will feature graphic posters summarizing the students' wor
 k. The show is open to the University community and the public. We encour
 age people to join us to celebrate and see how interior design unites hum
 anity.
X-ALT-DESC;FMTTYPE=text/html:<p>  For the last 15 weeks\, students have d
 eveloped designs for tenants in a hypothetical community centerŌĆöfocusin
 g on the complexities of developing community\, supporting people across 
 populations\, ethically building\, and technically meet construction and 
 code requirements. The Capstone Show will feature graphic posters summari
 zing the students' work. The show is open to the University community and
  the public. We encourage people to join us to celebrate and see how inte
 rior design unites humanity.</p>
